{{! ---
component: rich-text-editor (rte)
============================================

Requirements:

Options:
- rteContextClass {String} [default] - Just pass a string
- rteClasses {String} - Modifier classes
- rteMd {String} - Path to markdown file (starting at the root directory)
- rtes {Array} - You can pass an array to this component which consists of multiple rteMD
- rtes.rteMd {String} - Path to markdown file (starting at the root directory)

Important Notes:
This component should be used most of the time for content editor sections

--- }}
<div class="c-rte{{#if rteContextClass}}--{{rteContextClass}}{{else}}--default{{/if}}{{#if rteClasses}} {{rteClasses}}{{/if}}" data-css="c-rte">
	{{#if rteMd}}
		{{md rteMd}}
	{{/if}}

	{{#if rtes}}
		{{#each rtes}}
			{{md rteMd}}
		{{/each}}
	{{/if}}
</div>